# no.Diet Project Overview

## Tech Stack

- **Framework**: Next.js 16 (App Router) + React 19 + TypeScript (strict mode)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4 + CSS custom properties
- **State**: React Context (`QuizProvider` / `useQuiz()`) + localStorage persistence
- **Fonts**: DM Serif Display (headings) + DM Sans (body) via `next/font`

## Architecture

This is a **client-side only** quiz funnel application:
- No backend, API routes, or database
- No authentication (email capture only)
- All pages use `"use client"` directive
- State persists to localStorage automatically

## Key Files

- `lib/quiz-context.tsx` — React Context provider with `useQuiz()` hook
- `lib/quiz-data.ts` — Quiz questions, types (`Answers`, `Gender`), and constants
- `lib/generate-analysis.ts` — BMI and body analysis calculations
- `app/globals.css` — Design tokens (CSS variables) and custom animations

## Path Alias

Use `@/*` to import from the project root:

```typescript
import { useQuiz } from "@/lib/quiz-context";
```

## Route Structure

- `/` — Landing page (gender selection)
- `/quiz` — Multi-step quiz flow
- `/email` — Email capture
- `/summary` — Personalized results
- `/offer/*` — Pricing and discount pages
